Fourth Department,

October, 1947.

(October 1, 1947.) In the Matter of the Accounting of Lincoln Rochester Trust Company, as Substitute Trustee under the Will of Jennie W. Force, Deceased, Respondent. John W. Force, as Executor of Jennie W. Force, Deceased, Appellant; J. Kirby Post, as Administrator of the Estate of Gertrude F. Post, Deceased, Respondent.

Respondent. Motion for reargument denied; motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Harris, McCurn, Larkin and Love, JJ. [See 271 App. Div. 948.]
